Go behind-the-scenes on the first ever #MWII Raid 🎯

Boss fights. Hellscapes. Underwater mazes. It’s unlike anything we’ve done before.

Your Shipment has arrived 🚢📦

Deliver mayhem on this reimagined close-quarter classic plus more in the Season 01 Reloaded free content update, available now.

Merry Shipmas to all, and to all a good fight 🎄
 
Happy holidays from IW (and definitely Klaus!)
We'll be sharing more updates about #MWII and #WZ2 in the lead-up to our deep-dive blog. 👀

Battle Royale looting changes, and many more, are coming with Season 02!

Player eliminations and all loot containers will now pop floating loot out onto the floor!
 
See more in next week’s studio blog.

New missions, new Exclusion Zone and difficulty tuning.
 
Prepare for DMZ’s Season 02 update with our deep-dive blog next week.

No HUD? No problem. Hardcore is back!

Follow Season 02’s Multiplayer updates in our studio blog later this week.

Make some room in your wallets! 

More cash and lower prices are coming to Warzone 2 in Season 02!

💰📈

Interested in joining the team? New roles are available at IW Austin! Openings include Engineering opportunities in Gameplay, AI, UI, and Networking. To find out more information on these roles, head over to our LinkedIn Page.

From unforgettable memories on immersive battlegrounds to real world friends and late night games, here’s to 20 years of staying frosty.

Thank you to all the players for making this adventure so special #CODNext

Drop into Call of Duty: Warzone with a soundtrack as epic as the action.

The official soundtrack for Modern Warfare 2 | Warzone by @jasongravesmusic is out now 🎵

“Your time on the altar will come soon enough.”

20 years of @callofduty. 20 years of staying frosty. 20 years of “one more match” with the squad. 

Thank you for everything these last 20 years. Here’s to many more 🫡 

#COD20

The Haunting has been a labor of love from all of us here at Infinity Ward. 

We're thrilled you are enjoying the event, and wish you all a very Happy Halloween! 💀🎃

Meet some of the talented team at Infinity Ward Mexico! Based in Mexico City, they’re just one of our Infinity Ward studios around the globe. Here’s how they gave El Asilo a Dia de Muertos makeover for the Haunting 💀
THANK YOU to the #DMZ community for making the Beta so special.
My family dragging me out of bed at 6am on Christmas morning.
As 2024 begins, we want to say thank you to the Players who spent 2023 alongside us for six huge Seasons. From everyone at Infinity Ward, have a safe and happy New Year! 🎉
